strategy: This matchup is pretty easy, just do your best to not let him poke you with his W or AAs. Most ASols will opt to push and roam, so just farm and ping him mia so your team doesn't die to his roams. You can dodge his Q with proper usage of your E and/or your Q3. When he ults you, you can ult as well and you will not be knocked back because you hit him with it.
